{"id": 2060, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常生活中，你都因为“装东西”而遇到过哪些困扰？", "description": "那些被你容忍多时的容器难题。", "record_count": 2596, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171212114913emrUsKiVZ41jJEO8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-15T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 254467, "content": "衣柜的衣服叠好了，想拿出放在底下的衬衫上面的容易全乱了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 440, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 254468, "content": "装孙子的时候心里总是很不爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 254, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370271}, {"id": 254470, "content": "大部分主打极简风的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686351}, {"id": 254726, "content": "回家行李箱塞不下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860346}, {"id": 254471, "content": "出差时背书包不够装 拖行李箱又太大而且也不方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 194, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656714}, {"id": 254474, "content": "杯子里面只装白开水。。因为要是装其他的液体就会要洗杯子（懒到无可救药 逃", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 254475, "content": "书籍奇奇怪怪的尺寸内页却是没什么用的大面积留白，大小不一摆放既不美观又很浪费书架的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 254476, "content": "装无所谓，装你说的对，装开心，装懂了，装孙子，装你妹！", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 254734, "content": "一些小物件觉得很难收拾，不知道该怎么归类，到放哪儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096902}, {"id": 254479, "content": "世界上有三件事情装不了，不爱一个人，睡觉，举止自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213720}, {"id": 254480, "content": "给爱车买了车罩，可是简单收起来后却占了大半个后备箱", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183306}, {"id": 254736, "content": "强行装x失败…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704757}, {"id": 254481, "content": "收纳盒什么的有用？买了一堆收纳的，理完后，过一段时间东西照样乱放，还多了一堆收纳盒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213733}, {"id": 254484, "content": "想不到什么新颖又低调的装逼新法而苦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 254742, "content": "不带包的时候，钥匙单独装裤兜或者衣兜里（无拉链）总容易丢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215481}, {"id": 254743, "content": "装东西很麻烦的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 254491, "content": "和陌生人约炮怎样选择套套的尺寸？", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 254760, "content": "笔袋里总是装不下考试答案", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959329}, {"id": 256041, "content": "总是会觉得，装是为了美观和方便，可是事实更加麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1193677}, {"id": 254766, "content": "不习惯带钱包，装现金总是一卷……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215682}, {"id": 254515, "content": "装*…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 254772, "content": "每次去超市买东西都忘记带购物袋，所以总是要花钱买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215809}, {"id": 254517, "content": "一定要说！！！口袋看起来不浅然而骑车时候手机掉出来，把手机屏摔的稀烂?", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125750}, {"id": 254519, "content": "小时候心里装了好多好多梦想，身体长大了心却变小了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213805}, {"id": 254522, "content": "因工作需要每天背电脑上下班，永远买不到又时尚又能装电脑的包包，打扮得美美的，却背着个丑包，整体风格太不搭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206195}, {"id": 254532, "content": "当然是装电池、牙刷之类的包装盒啊！纸板上这个半圆洞，尤其是旁边的虚线根本没发挥过作用。如果身边没有剪刀，每次都只能靠暴力拆解，手指头都抠疼还不一定抠得出来。。。", "image": "img/option/option/20171215141753a1oRW72NUzqlTGKf", "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211379}, {"id": 254533, "content": "箱子不够大", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131307}, {"id": 254534, "content": "白嫩嫩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188810}, {"id": 254793, "content": "绝对分类", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725092}, {"id": 254540, "content": "分类", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208996}, {"id": 254541, "content": "脑子不够大，装不下那么多的是是非非！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 11479}, {"id": 254542, "content": "强迫症会在放收纳盒的那层柜子里，想方设法地充分利用剩余空间，于是又塞满了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213866}, {"id": 254543, "content": "收纳盒四角的圆边总是很让人苦恼地变成空白地带，只做成方方正正的不是更好吗 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213874}, {"id": 254544, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206116}, {"id": 254545, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206116}, {"id": 254548, "content": "好装不好拿  拿了装好的一切都毁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212302}, {"id": 255060, "content": "书包里总是会攒越来越多的废纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854939}, {"id": 254549, "content": "落灰?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210712}, {"id": 254551, "content": "蒸汽熨斗为什么不能多装水？？？？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213902}, {"id": 254810, "content": "该怎么宠你？我的耳机宝宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216073}, {"id": 254811, "content": "湿漉漉的伞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216073}, {"id": 254567, "content": "想起一件好久没穿的衣服，翻箱倒柜没找到，最后重新整理才想起来，它在另一个箱子里", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213941}, {"id": 255081, "content": "东西和盒子一样大，就差那么一点放不下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0,